// Embedder service contract.
//
// The embedder is a Python gRPC server backed by vLLM serving BGE-M3 on
// the user's TrueNAS GPU. It supports bidirectional streaming so the
// processor can pipeline chunk batches without head-of-line blocking, and
// so the scorer's vector sub-scorer can amortize the round-trip when
